1
00:00:02,984 --> 00:00:04,885
Leonard, tu es sous la douche ?

2
00:00:04,886 --> 00:00:08,022
Je ne t'entend pas !
Je suis sous la douche !

3
00:00:08,023 --> 00:00:10,157
Je te demandais si tu
etais dans la douche,

4
00:00:10,158 --> 00:00:12,126
mais c'est accessoire maintenant!

5
00:00:12,127 --> 00:00:13,294
Quoi ?

6
00:00:13,295 --> 00:00:18,132
Accessoire! Rendu non important
par des informations plus recentes!

7
00:00:18,133 --> 00:00:20,684
Je ne t'entend pas !
Je suis sous la douche !

8
00:00:20,685 --> 00:00:22,503
Je dois laisser tomber
les enfantillages.

9
00:00:22,504 --> 00:00:23,771
Urgence.

10
00:00:23,772 --> 00:00:25,639
Quel genre
d'urgence?

11
00:00:25,640 --> 00:00:28,275
Mathematiquement--
32 grammes de jus de banane,

12
00:00:28,276 --> 00:00:30,344
16 grammes d'urée.

13
00:00:30,345 --> 00:00:32,913
Tu ne vas pas faire ça là?

14
00:00:32,914 --> 00:00:34,648
Oh si je t'assure.

15
00:00:34,649 --> 00:00:37,251
Sheldon, je ne suis pas tout seul ici.

16
00:00:37,252 --> 00:00:39,203
Quoi?!

17
00:00:40,088 --> 00:00:42,056
Bonjour, Sheldon.

18
00:00:42,057 --> 00:00:43,524
Qu'est-ce que tu fais ici?

19
00:00:43,525 --> 00:00:44,792
Elle n'a pas le droit d'etre la!

20
00:00:44,793 --> 00:00:47,461
<i>Nous etions la les premiers; donc
tu ne dois pas etre la.</i>

21
00:00:47,462 --> 00:00:49,129
Selon l'accord de colocation

22
00:00:49,130 --> 00:00:50,598
paragraphe 9, sous-section B,

23
00:00:50,599 --> 00:00:52,333
"Le droit
la une vie privee dans la salle de bain

24
00:00:52,334 --> 00:00:54,635
est suspendu dans un cas de force majeure."

25
00:00:54,636 --> 00:00:56,303
Et crois moi,
c'est le cas

26
00:00:56,304 --> 00:00:59,240
<i>un tres grand cas de force majeure.</i>

27
00:00:59,241 --> 00:01:01,742
Aller, tu peux pas
attendre deux minutes ?

28
00:01:01,743 --> 00:01:04,678
Allons, Leonard,
laisse le gars faire pipi.

29
00:01:09,417 --> 00:01:12,119
Penny? Penny?

30
00:01:12,120 --> 00:01:13,787
Penny?

31
00:01:13,788 --> 00:01:15,188
Quoi?

32
00:01:15,189 --> 00:01:17,391
Bouge. Bouge. Bouge!

33
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:22,580
? Our whole universe
was in a hot, dense state ?

34
00:01:22,581 --> 00:01:25,899
? Then nearly 14 billion years
ago expansion started... Wait! ?

35
00:01:25,900 --> 00:01:27,418
? The Earth began to cool ?

36
00:01:27,419 --> 00:01:30,271
? The autotrophs began to drool,
Neanderthals developed tools ?

37
00:01:30,272 --> 00:01:32,773
<i>? We built the Wall ?
? We built the pyramids ?</i>

38
00:01:32,774 --> 00:01:34,892
? Math, Science, History,
unraveling the mystery ?

39
00:01:34,893 --> 00:01:36,877
? That all started
with a big bang ?

40
00:01:36,878 --> 00:01:38,135
<i>? Bang! ?</i>

41
00:01:38,160 --> 00:01:42,160
<font color=#00FF00>? The Big Bang Theory 4x21 ?</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>The Agreement Dissection</font>
